==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grugru worm
<hw>Gru"gru worm"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The larva
or grub of a large South American beetle (<spn>Calandra palmarum</spn>),
which lives in the pith of palm trees and sugar cane. It is eaten by the
natives, and esteemed a delicacy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gruidae</ent>⟦br⟧
